snippet.title: Hannah Montana Rock Out the Show - PSP™
snippet.description:
http://eu.playstation.com/psp/games/detail/item157805/Hannah-Montana-Rock-Out-the-Show/

In the first ever Hannah Montana game for PSP, fans will not only star in the show, they will also design a custom concert in each city they visit and rock the stage as Hannah Montana with 11 hit songs.

Jackson and Lilly join in on the fun to help Hannah on her tour as they travel to seven amazing locations around the world and customise outfits, design stages and so much more.
